snippet.title: Elansar
snippet.description:
Elansar is a small myst like "point & click" adventure game. Explore an island and solve puzzles. Will you uncover the Island's mystery ?
Available on Steam Greenlight, itch.io, Android, Jaguar CD & Dreamcast !
http://onorisoft.free.fr/retroshop/index.html#Elansar
